  "texts": [
    "Experiment of (a-g) and (I) had been repeated at least three times with similar results.",
    "Source data are provided as a Source Data file.",
    "(h) was created with BioRender.com.",
    "shown in Fig. 2g, RAD18-ablation and BER inhibition had synergistic effects on TMZ sensitivity in U373 cells.",
    "Therefore, in MGMT-deficient cells (in which the main cytotoxic lesion is O 6 mG), BER and RAD18 participate in distinct pathways for tolerance of TMZ-induced lesions."
